CustomField.description: This field will be used by Bullseye to determine what Geo codes will be used for Rep Locator Tool. If Checked - Use value in BGAMob_Geo_Code for Rep Locator. If Unchecked - Bullseye will try to automatically Geo code based on address
CustomField.inlineHelpText: This field will be used by Bullseye to determine what Geo codes will be used for Rep Locator Tool.
CustomField.label: Use Manual Geo codes
